{"tid":2311601,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"做空Tesla五年終減倉，聲稱“做空很痛苦，馬斯克幹得好”","createTime":"2020-12-04T07:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:08:13.000Z","uid":219488,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"05dc249e493e28cb90ceeaad72a4dcc6dd29cc40","tid":2311601,"uid":219488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"智通財經APP獲悉，華爾街著名空頭Jim Chanos自2016年以來一直做空特斯拉 (NASDAQ:TSLA)股票，但現在他已經減持了空頭頭寸。<br />\n<br />\nJim Chanos此前以最大的力度做空特斯拉，他旗下的對衝基金公司Kynikos Associates對這隻股票的空頭頭寸爲5%，這是對一隻股票進行做空的最高限額，但現在他已經減持了特斯拉空頭。Jim Chanos表示：&ldquo;很明顯，這是很痛苦的經歷。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這位看空者的態度轉變發生特斯拉在12月21日進入標普500之前。<br />\n<br />\nJim Chanos在採訪中稱，在最初的四年裏，做空特斯拉交易從短線上來看的表現並不是很糟糕，當時這家電動汽車製造商的股票並沒有跑贏大盤。<br />\n他表示從未與特斯拉首席執行官埃隆&middot;馬斯克(Elon Musk)見過面或交談過，但如果他們見面，他會說&ldquo;到目前爲止工作乾得很好&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nJim Chanos曾在2017年聲稱，&ldquo;特斯拉顯然未按一家汽車公司進行估值，而是按馬斯克的價值，他纔是人們持有股票的原因。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n金融分析公司S3 Partners數據顯示，特斯拉目前的空頭權益爲273.7億美元，佔其已發行股票的6.35%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hk.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/article-127795?utm_source=responsys&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=Editorial_DailyDigest_Multilang_LIVE_04/12/2020&amp;utm_content=cta_button\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hk.investing.com%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-news%2Farticle-127795%3Futm_source%3Dresponsys%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3DEditorial_DailyDigest_Multilang_LIVE_04%2F12%2F2020%26utm_content%3Dcta_button&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a0472cb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hk.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/article-127795?utm_source=responsys&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=Editorial_DailyDigest_Multilang_LIVE_04/12/2020&amp;utm_content=cta_button</a>"},{"pid":"9b7c91cea252262915e0e7ef876de67721e9f0a3","tid":2311601,"uid":70521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"唔知蝕左幾多呢"},{"pid":"68a9a2c7008407093a5a2479976c6a6b2078c6a9","